Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼幹的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來  真是受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  這種程度的陷阱我就中一個好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正獵物還是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了  中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  猛吃了一棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這魚是午飯的材料的說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有別的材料了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的哦  是阪本說他想吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小鬼胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你吃掉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}回去的時候去嘗嘗車站前的冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘是不是很想去上學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是突然怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人說名乃要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  這是誰告訴你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的可不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你是不是要去別的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有準備上午去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯的材料又給弄沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士我也要去也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我什麼也不會給你買的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買鯊魚巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會買的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買吧  鯊魚巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:50.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我都說了不會買的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買吧  買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會買的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本都說了要買
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼了祐子  搖搖晃晃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上起來後就被這麼說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你不覺得你的語言結構崩壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像發燒了的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼拖著一副這樣的身體來學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就有說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想給你們看我的魔術表演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.75,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(400,00)}日\N常\N之\N53
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是第一次聽到這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  現在可不是說什麼魔術的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是好不容易練習了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看到我的魔術表演絕對會大吃一驚的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我現在就有嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你先坐下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的魔術道具…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被我看光了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我就裝作什麼都沒有看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她是拖著這副身子來學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要變大型魔術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出出出出  出來了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道具都跑出來了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面巾紙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼我就開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O…OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她都幹了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先藏起來再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就先來變…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有注意到鴿子和手杖不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有多虛弱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我用香煙穿過百円硬幣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面開了個洞啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是紅心A
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才  有什麼東西從嘴裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了什麼樣的機關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在請你安眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.68,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(400,00)}日\N常\N之\N54
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就去超市了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  博士我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你使壞了  我今天什麼都不會給你買的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本你好可憐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說你這傢伙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃要買什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再買一條魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士要買什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  博士今天不能給你買東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  那麼我就不買零食
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食以外的東西今天也不能買哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話搞得我不知道買什麼好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是想買東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鯊魚蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  名乃  是鯊魚蛋糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺了小攤出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃  要不要買來吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不能買零食哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  我只是想買給阪本作為禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為阪本先生和你一樣不聽話  所以不能買
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是想買給名乃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能買就是不能買
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這裡嬌慣了她的話  下次又會做同樣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了博士  要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:15.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}給我買  給我買  給我買…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡要硬著心腸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  果然還是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}給我買  給我買  給我買…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}給我買  給我買  給我買…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微買一點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:29.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}給我買  給我買  給我買…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}給我買  給我買  給我買…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}給我買  給我買  給我買…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  結果還是買了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我敗給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是脾氣不好又任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是該管一管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鬼  你差不多該學會忍耐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你個大頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東雲家今天也很和平
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
