Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  80分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真做的話不是能做得很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼  這個的高分的秘訣是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  秘訣什麼的  才沒有呢  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  告訴我秘訣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80分  好嘞  80分  好嘞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:41.65,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,260)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}秘\N\N\N訣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我告訴你得80分的秘訣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要啦  我得了96分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80分  那可是需要不間斷的努力與
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:01.67,title-W,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fad(1000,0)\an8}還算過得去的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚嗚嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:45.71,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,270)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}現\N\N\N實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我來給你做飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她還在旅行中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安  小實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  今天就專心陪孫子玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉讓人厭煩的現實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小實  今天要玩點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外公外公  比起那個  印章在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  印章在哪裡  藏在哪裡了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個書架裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  印章在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  會在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:25.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這比現實更加的冷酷無情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪在哪  快給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是慢啊  你以為碰面的時間是幾點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  本來是要坐巴士來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:12:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻搭上了以時代為名的潮流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣子去步行街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:17.36,title-W,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,300)\fad(400,600)}日\N常\N之\N55
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  名乃  名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腫麼了  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一點想去尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  名乃  好不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  你搞錯了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅宋湯是一種食物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去尿尿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  名乃  名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  只有漏出一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你先快點去廁所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因擔憂而沒有說話的阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小鬼就是麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是在這樣一個刮著暴風的深夜不敢獨自去廁所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她就是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就讓我來陪她去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這傢伙再次認識到我的重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦吧  讓我陪你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本這麼小  看起來很弱的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘是不是很想去上學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡到這邊來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  一起去尿尿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是很想尿尿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有一點點害怕  你就陪我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你把我叫起來不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫了你好多次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在咚咚地響  也許有人過來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是屋頂上的煙囪在響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這雨可真是大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  名乃  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打雷了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有博士在  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去尿完  然後回到被子裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  雖說一個人去是有點害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去的話就感覺沒那麼怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你想去上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的  我會一直待在家裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阪本說名乃想去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥到掉渣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80分！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:17.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(600,600)}一句話時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管一個月很快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是星期天卻很遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.96,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,300)\fad(600,600)}激\N情\N高\N漲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是80分  80分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口在右側
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唱80年代的歌給你聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只唱到80分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80分  好嘞  80分  好嘞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾回你的伊甸園啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.91,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,290)\fad(00,00)\bord15\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}伊\N\N甸\N\N園
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快點安靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面宣佈這次的平均得分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是92分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不要說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你突然發什麼顛啊小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在這裡玩  快幫忙把衣服收拾好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始你就去上學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼  怎麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是博士我為你著想而做出的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話白天我吃一堆零食她也不會生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個樣子的話不是沒辦法背小學生書包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去讀高中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把發條取下來的話就去不了學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是名乃的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃名乃名乃名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士博士博士博士博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃名乃名乃名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士博士博士博士博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃名乃名乃名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士博士博士博士博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是萬國旗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常可以聽到「ばんこっき」和「ばんこくき」兩種發音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩種好像都是正確的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不要在意這種小事」
